\begin_layout Example
Obtenga los valores de 
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

 e 
\begin_inset Formula $y$
\end_inset

 tales que es valor de 
\begin_inset Formula $2x-y^{2}$
\end_inset

 sea mínimo, si 
\begin_inset Formula $x^{2}+3y^{2}=9.$
\end_inset

 
